Igor Use-Cases:
---------------

1. Copy one file from A to B and rename it to C.
2. Execute a Shell Script A at machine B.
3. Copy the newest file, which has not already been transferred, from A to B. Send a message C with the filename.
4. Select from database A, convert the data to format B and send it as message C.
5. Select from database A, convert the data to format B and write it to a ZIP file


